NoMotionVectors: No motion vectors will be present in the geometry cache.
ImportAbcVelocitiesAsMotionVectors: Imports the Velocities from the Alembic file and converts them to motion vectors. This will increase file size as the motion vectors will be stored on disc.
CalculateMotionVectorsDuringImport: Force calculation of motion vectors during import. This will increase file size as the motion vectors will be stored on disc.
